      <h1 style="font-size:2rem;line-height:1.35;">The Fed Says AI Success Could Mean Rate Hikes, Failure Means Stagflation — Same Logic Behind Both Extremes</h1>
      <div class="article-meta">
        <span>2026-05-10</span>
        {tags.filter(Boolean).map(t => <span class="tag">{t}</span>)}
